      <title>别被愚弄了，雪已成为过去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-01-08/winter-storm-aside-snow-is-disappearing-because-of-climate-change</link>
      <description><![CDATA[暴风雨将会持续发生，但长期趋势是冬季变暖、降雪减少，这将带来水资源短缺和经济活动损失等严重后果。]]></description>
